        <h1>Pressure Washing Marketing in Miami: SEO vs Google Ads</h1>
        <p class="lead">SEO and Google Ads do different jobs for a pressure washing company. One books jobs this week, the other compounds for years. Here is the honest math on each for the Miami market, and the hybrid that beats picking one.</p>
        <div class="post-meta">
