          <span>8 min read</span>
          <span>Local SEO</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        class="hero-cover"
        src="/blog/hero-pressure-washing-seo-vs-ads.webp"
        alt="Split scene of a Miami pressure washing job and a phone showing local search results, sunny South Florida driveway being cleaned"
