              <tr><td>Cost model</td><td>Per click (~$5) or per lead (LSA)</td><td>Flat monthly, free per job once ranking</td></tr>
              <tr><td>When you stop paying</td><td>Calls stop within 24 hours</td><td>Rankings and jobs continue</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Compounds over time</td><td>No</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Best for</td><td>Now, seasonal spikes, post-storm</td><td>Durable pipeline, recurring accounts</td></tr>
              <tr class="highlight"><td><strong>Miami difficulty</strong></td><td><strong>Moderate competition</strong></td><td><strong>Low, unusually winnable</strong></td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
